name: Symbol
intro: The Layer 1 blockchain of the open source hybrid public chain and privately linked New Economic Movement (NEM) project
introduce: Symbol (XYM) is a layer-one blockchain that is the project of New Economic Movement (NEM). Symbol is the next iteration of NEM’s N1S1 blockchain, which is an open-source hybrid private and public blockchain with a focus on enterprise use cases. Its primary use case is to help businesses cut costs, reduce complexities, and streamline innovation.
